OL,6,FA senior judge has rejected a bid to
OL,7,Fhave the cases against three men
OL,8,Faccused of murdering east Belfast man
OL,9,FIan Ogle dismissed.
OL,11,FFollowing Mr Justice McFarland's
OL,12,Fruling, barristers representing the
OL,13,Ftrio revealed none of the defendants
OL,14,Fwould be giving evidence and that no
OL,15,Fevidence would be called on their
OL,16,Fbehalf.
