OL,3,CIan Ogle murder accused lose bid to
OL,4,Chave case dismissed
OL,6,FMr Ogle, a 45-year old father-of-two,
OL,7,Fwas beaten and stabbed a total of 11
OL,8,Ftimes yards from his Cluan Place home
OL,9,Fat around 9.20pm on Sunday January 27,
OL,10,F2019.
OL,12,FIn July, barristers acting on behalf
OL,13,Fof Walter Ervine (43), 38-year old
OL,14,FGlenn Rainey and Robert Spiers (41)
OL,15,Flaunched 'no case to answer'
OL,16,Fapplications on the grounds there was
OL,17,Finsufficient evidence to proceed any
OL,18,Ffurther.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
