OL,6,FThe applications were made at the
OL,7,Fconclusion of the Crown's case and Mr
OL,8,FJustice McFarland gave his ruling at
OL,9,FBelfast Crown Court on Monday.
OL,11,FIt's the Crown's case that two minutes
OL,12,Fbefore the attack, CCTV from a Glider
OL,13,Fbus on the Albertbridge Road captured
OL,14,Fa group of five men walking towards
OL,15,FCluan Place - and that these five were
OL,16,Finvolved in the fatal assault.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
