OL,6,FEarlier this year, Jonathan Brown (39)
OL,7,Ffrom Whinney Hill in Dundonald and 45-
OL,8,Fyear old Mark Sewell of of Glenmount
OL,9,FDrive in Newtownabbey were handed life
OL,10,Fsentences after they pleaded guilty to
OL,11,Fmurdering Mr Ogle.
OL,13,FGlenn Rainey (38) whose address was
OL,14,Fgiven as Ballyhalbert Caravan Park,
OL,15,FWalter Irvine (43) from Litchfield
OL,16,FStreet in Belfast and 41-year old
OL,17,FRobert Spiers from Millars Park in
OL,18,FDundonald all denied the charge and
OL,19,Fwere the subject of a non-jury trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
