OL,6,FDuring the trial, the Crown made the
OL,7,Fcase that Rainey and Ervine were
OL,8,Finvolved in an incident at the Prince
OL,9,FAlbert bar with Mr Ogle's son Ryan
OL,10,FJohnston in July 2017.
OL,12,FThe Crown also cited an attack meted
OL,13,Fout on a local man by Ryan Johnston
OL,14,Fand his father Ian Ogle hours before
OL,15,Fthe murder as a motive for revenge.
