OL,6,FThe Crown's evidence against Rainey
OL,7,Fincluded his mobile phone activity
OL,8,Fwith his co-accused on the night of
OL,9,Fthe murder, his DNA being found on the
OL,10,Fdoor handle of car the prosecution say
OL,11,Fwas used to transport those involved
OL,12,Fin the murder and his travel to
OL,13,FThailand in the aftermath of the fatal
OL,14,Fattack.
