OL,6,FIn addition, it's the Crown's case
OL,7,Fthat the clothing worn by 'male three'
OL,8,Fin the footage recorded on the Glider
OL,9,Fcamera was similar to clothing worn by
OL,10,FRainey when he visited a bank in the
OL,11,Fcentre of Belfast four days before the
OL,12,Fmurder.
OL,14,FIn their application that Rainey had
OL,15,F'no case to answer', his defence team
OL,16,Fsubmitted that following the July 2017
OL,17,Fbar incident, there was no evidence of
OL,18,Fongoing issues between him and Ian
OL,19,FOgle.
