OL,9,Fand that a man who they say could have
OL,10,Fbeen Ervine was seen cycling along Wye
OL,11,FStreet and dismounting from his bike
OL,12,Fin a similar method used by Ervine
OL,13,Fwhen he was captured on CCTV on a shop
OL,14,Fon the Newtownards Road earlier that
OL,15,Fmonth.
