OL,6,FDuring the trial, the Crown said
OL,7,FErvine was the 'lead male' caught on
OL,8,Fthe Glider footage and that the
OL,9,Fclothes that male wore were similar to
OL,10,Fclothes worn by Ervine earlier that
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,FRegarding his 'no case to answer'
OL,14,Fapplication, Ervine's barrister
OL,15,Fpointed out the way he dismounted a
OL,16,Fbicycle was 'not unique' and that the
OL,17,Fmotivation for using mobile phone
OL,18,Fusage on the night of the murder was
OL,19,F'pure speculation.'
