OL,6,FIn an application to have the charge
OL,7,Fagainst Spiers dismissed, his
OL,8,Fbarrister argued that the Ernesto
OL,9,Fknife set was widely available to buy
OL,10,Fand there was no evidence to link the
OL,11,Fknife found in the river to the murder.
OL,13,FHis legal team also argued there was
OL,14,Fno evidence of ill feeling between
OL,15,FSpiers and Mr Ogle, and that when he
OL,16,Fwas arrested he co-operated with
OL,17,Fpolice.
